---
title: Mintables NFT Generator How to - Make either layer A or layer B to show up?
date: 2022-11-28T07:24:35.572Z
description: How to use Mintables NFT generator to display different shapes and
  styles of artwork
image: img/display_layers.jpg
---
When displaying different shapes and styles of artwork, creators frequently want to display a different set of image layers; for example, the [RENJI M1](https://www.mintables.club/m/renji) project, which is available on Mintables, has three entirely different base skins (check the hand gestures).﻿

![RENJI M1 NFT Art](data:image/jpeg;base64, "RENJI M1 NFT Art")

﻿\
\
By selecting the + Group button and separating your layers on Mintables, you can create various groups to achieve this.﻿

![NFT Groups](https://i0.wp.com/info.mintables.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image-1.png?resize=980%2C635&ssl=1 "NFT Groups")

﻿\
\
There can be a wide range of layers among various groups. By doing this, you'll be able to include various collections of artwork in one. 

Different groups can have completely different layers. This will allow you to have different sets of artwork in the same collection.
